name: Ludmilla El Golilla - HEartN #8
description:
Ludmilla is a primate that loves to change look and to get crazy when the music hits!
!!SOUND ON!!
This is the 8# NFT of a ongoing collection!

After HEN went down, Ludmilla felt very sad and needed a rehab. This was all so confusing, the place what once powered her heart, vanished in the abiss of memories.
As the time passed, a light reappeared in this beatiful movement. Probably it will never be the same, but we are here all together feeding this light.

With this NFT I want to say thank you to all the people that made this journey so beautiful and special!
Thanks to the people that are keeping HEN alive!
And a special thanks to the creator and inventor of all of this, Rafael you created something very special! With my biggest respect I can only say thank you!

///HEN Community Thank You Token///
